interpretation:
The "multiply" card represented by the ✖️ emoji indicates a time of growth and expansion. This card suggests that you may need to take on more responsibilities or tackle more challenges, but it also promises great rewards. This card may also indicate that you need to multiply your efforts in order to achieve your goals.

The "multiply" card can also represent a time of abundance and prosperity. This card suggests that you will be rewarded for your hard work and dedication, and that your efforts will yield a bountiful harvest. This card encourages you to continue to invest in yourself and your goals, as the rewards will be significant.

Associated keywords for the "multiply" card include growth, expansion, abundance, prosperity, effort, dedication, and rewards. When this card appears in a reading, it is important to remember that hard work and persistence will pay off, and that you should continue to invest in your goals in order to achieve success.
